ttom: 2rem;\n    }\n\n    /* team grid */\n    .team-grid {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      gap: 40px;\n      justify-content: center;\n      margin-top: 40px;\n    }\n    .team-member {\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n    .team-member img {\n      width: 200px;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <!-- Our Story -->\n  <h2 class=\"large\">Our Story</h2>\n  <p>\n    Rugtomize was born from five generations of Persian rug craftsmanship and a rebellious drive to shake things up. We saw a market flooded with cookie-cutter home décor – so we built something different. A fully personalized, design-first rug platform where creativity isn’t optional – it’s the whole point.\n  </p>\n\n  <!-- Image Row -->\n  <div class=\"about-img-row\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0766/1840/0065/files/SNORLAX_8a840c3d-55fa-4066-809d-2bddcd52f78a.jpg?v=1704841425\" alt=\"Rug example 1\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0766/1840/0065/files/gempages_547641604358276043-8f4f7ca0-b143-4a06-9ccd-7157ddb2597c.jpg?v=1735963548\" alt=\"Rug being crafted\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0766/1840/0065/files/IMG_9547_1.jpg?v=1752017879\" alt=\"Rug material\">\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Built In California -->\n  <h2 class=\"medium\">Built in California, Backed by Innovation</h2>\n  <p>\n    Everything is made in our vertically integrated facility in Orange County. Our team blends heritage craftsmanship with modern tech to create ultra-high resolution custom rugs, made for businesses, collectors, and creatives alike.\n  </p>\n\n  <!-- Blockquote -->\n  <blockquote>\n    <em>“Weaving Dreams: The Rugtomize Journey” – From pandemic pivots to the Woven show, we’ve turned challenges into breakthroughs. What started as an idea in a family shop became a movement to turn rugs into a medium of self-expression and branding.</em>\n  </blockquote>\n\n  <p>\n    With clients like Netflix, Spotify, and Disney on board, Rugtomize is scaling fast – and still obsessed with the details. Our platform gives anyone the tools to design, approve, and receive a one-of-a-kind rug. All we need is your vision.\n  </p>\n\n  <a href=\"/collections/all-custom-rugs\" class=\"about-cta\">Shop Custom Rugs</a>\n\n  <!-- Mission & Vision -->\n  <h2>Our Mission</h2>\n  <p>\n    To innovate the rug-making process, making limitless customization accessible – faster, more affordable, and built around identity. We’re here to help people express who they are from the ground up.\n  </p>\n\n  <h2>Our Vision</h2>\n  <p>\n    Rugs should speak. Our vision is to transform rugs into personal statements – merging art, branding, and identity underfoot.\n  </p>\n\n  <!-- Video -->\n  <div style=\"margin: 40px 0;\">\n    <video autoplay muted playsinline style=\"width:100%; border-radius:8px;\">\n      <source src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/bb1d06c113ed416f97bc8e8b37b255ff.mp4\">\n      Your browser does not support the video tag.\n    </video>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Secondary blockquote -->\n  <blockquote class=\"secondary\">\n    <em>Our goal is to pioneer and reinvent the rug industry. For centuries, rugs have been hand-knotted by tradition. Now, we’re designing with precision, speed, and customization at scale – tailored to your taste.</em>\n  </blockquote>\n\n  <!-- Meet the Team -->\n  <h2>Meet the Team</h2>\n  <div class=\"team-grid\">\n    <div class=\"team-member\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0766/1840/0065/files/Founder.jpg?v=1721879168\" alt=\"Iman Nian\">\n      <div><strong>Iman Nian</strong><br>Founder</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"team-member\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0766/1840/0065/files/FullSizeRender.jpg?v=1686618701\" alt=\"John Sho\">\n      <div><strong>John Sho</strong><br>Production</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"team-member\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0766/1840/0065/files/